  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790100/extras/ae8346fbc66067ad3936c3c2b2f4e58a.webp?t=1733256054\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br>Step into the shoes of Everlyn Sterling, a new grad undertaking a temp job in a small town<strong> in dead winter</strong>. Little does she know this seemingly ordinary task will soon unveil a mysterious tale of a disturbed spirit. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790100/extras/f99c1194e3c905852939c5de2b70efd0.poster.avif?t=1733256054\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790100/extras/f99c1194e3c905852939c5de2b70efd0.webm?t=1733256054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Solve a series of brain teasers, booby traps, and ciphers set by the ghost. Can you unravel why a once beautiful mansion now harbors a dark, ugly secret?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790100/extras/d36e2f122f677664d8b7f6306b0f95d8.poster.avif?t=1733256054\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2790100/extras/d36e2f122f677664d8b7f6306b0f95d8.webm?t=1733256054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2></strong> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li> Simple point-and-click interface<br></li><li> Crack escape-room style puzzles <br></li><li> Explore a quiet haunted world with a minimalist art style <br></li><li> Make choices that impact your story progression and ending<br></li><li> Experience a scary and suspenseful story without gore or violence </li></ul>",
